/kref
/bin/
/.kref/
/.test-output/
# GoReleaser build output (snapshot and release artifacts).
/dist/
# MegaLinter run output. The "updated_sources" report drops partial copies of
# the tree here; leaving it tracked would poison `go vet ./...`, gofmt, and
# golangci-lint, which compile every non-dot directory under the module root.
/megalinter-reports/
/mega-linter.log
# Per-package Ginkgo JSON reports; the test wrapper archives and removes these,
# but an interrupted run can leave them scattered beside packages.
ginkgo-report.json
/.claude/handoff/
docs/superpowers/
# Planning material lives in kref's knowledge base, not the git tree. Any specs
# or plans regenerated under these paths stay local; ingest them with `kref`.
docs/dev/plans/
docs/dev/specs/
